*Visiore will be consumed in the following order: Free Visiore → Ordinary Visiore → Paid Visiore.

-Paid Visiore
Visiore purchased on each platform
*They cannot be transferred between or used on different platforms.

-Free Visiore
Visiore acquired as a bonus when buying Visiore on each platform.
*They cannot be transferred between or used on different platforms.

-Ordinary Visiore
Visiore obtained as a reward from logging in, completing missions, etc.
*They can be transferred between or used on different platforms.
